{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"db53697bd9","title":"给李鼎铭的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1b8ab7c133","index":0,"year":1944,"month":4,"day":29,"articleId":"db53697bd9"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji3","name":"毛泽东文集第三卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji3.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji3":{"comments":[{"id":"3bee7158da","publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"db53697bd9","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":4,"text":"李鼎铭（一八八一——一九四七），陕西米脂人。当时任陕甘宁边区政府副主席。"},{"id":"4c04a5f580","publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"db53697bd9","index":2,"part_index":2,"offset":49,"text":"李健侯，陕西米脂人。当时任陕甘宁边区参议会参议员，在米脂县文献委员会工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bebfa1d305","type":"title","text":"给李鼎铭的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"db53697bd9"},{"id":"3bee7158da","type":"appellation","text":"鼎铭老先生左右：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"db53697bd9"},{"id":"4c04a5f580","type":"paragraph","text":"《永昌演义》前数年为多人所借阅；近日鄙人阅读一过，获益良多。并已抄存一部，以为将来之用。作者李健侯先生经营此书，费了大力，请先生代我向作者致深切之敬意。此书赞美李自成个人品德，但贬抑其整个运动。实则吾国自秦以来二千余年推动社会向前进步者主要的是农民战争，大顺帝李自成将军所领导的伟大的农民战争，就是二千年来几十次这类战争中的极著名的一次。这个运动起自陕北，实为陕人的光荣，尤为先生及作者健侯先生们的光荣。此书如按上述新历史观点加以改造，极有教育人民的作用，未知能获作者同意否？又健侯先生近来健康如何，能来延安一游否？统祈转致健侯先生为祷！","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"db53697bd9"},{"id":"347a99f4ad","type":"paragraph","text":"敬颂大安！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"db53697bd9"},{"id":"da893e0d63","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"db53697bd9"},{"id":"545f16ca65","type":"paragraph","text":"四月二十九日","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"db53697bd9"},{"id":"746e99b206","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"db53697bd9"},{"id":"770f15e1de","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"db53697bd9"}],"page":{"id":"aad2dd5777","publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"db53697bd9","start":139,"end":139}}}},"__N_SSG":true}